Release 1.3:
- Added manual page.
- Better handling of multipart/alternative that contain multipart/alternative.
- Revised heuristic for choosing part of a multipart/alternative.

Release 1.2:
- When choosing part of a multipart/alternative, ignore pure text part
  if much smaller than HTML part.
- Added commands "dump" and "restore" to facilitate future evolution
  towards other database formats.

Release 1.1:
- Fixed "usage" message

Release 1.0:
- First public release
